==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Psychosis
<hw>Psy*cho"sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Psycho-</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Any vital action or activity.</def>
<rj><au>Mivart.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A disease of the mind; especially,
a functional mental disorder, that is, one unattended with evident
organic changes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Psychotherapeutics</ent>⟦br⟧
